<HEAD>With PM-Soviet-Georgia</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The State Department today supported the
demonstrations in Soviet Georgia and called on authorities to use
restraint in dealing with peaceful protests.
   ``What is at issue here is peaceful political expression,''
spokesman Richard Boucher said. ``We certainly support them in
that.''
   Boucher cited reports in Tass, the Soviet news agency, that 16
