<HEAD>Gregorian Awards Doctorate To Pinchas Zukerman</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PROVIDENCE, R.I. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Vartan Gregorian's first official act as
Brown University's 16th president was to surprise musician Pinchas
Zukerman with an honorary doctorate in music.
   Zukerman was the conductor and violin soloist at Gregorian's
inauguaral concert Sunday. Following the performance, Gregorian
appeared on stage and told Zukerman he had two surprises for him.
   ``If there is anything that unites us, it is music,'' Zukerman
said in accepting the honor.
